to solve the issue of isolated ai tools

MCP flips this. Developed as an open standard, it acts like a universal USB port for AI. Instead of writing separate code for every database, file system, or web service, MCP creates a secure, uniform protocol that lets an intelligence seamlessly read data (Resources), execute code (Tools), and follow logic (Prompts) across entirely different environments.

By leveraging MCP, we don't have to spend years building infrastructure from scratch. We use it as our backdoor to instantly plug into everything that already exists, but we wire it up to think and act with a 2035 mindset.

